data.description: A GREAT OPPORTUNITY AWAITS...To purchase an AFFORDABLE 4 BR Townhouse in Quakertown!!  You will find AMAZING upgrades completed in 2015.  A Beautiful Kitchen with high end custom cherry cabinetry & recessed lighting, Granite counters, a Tumble Stone back splash, Built in Microwave & Frigidaire Galley 5 burner smooth top stove & self cleaning oven!! Remodeled full baths & the security of a fenced yard. Large storage shed with electric remains,  Your LOW cost HOA offers trash& recycle collection, lighted parking, snow removal, common area maintenance & community pool. A RARE FIND IN THIS MARKET!!  DO NOT LOSE YOUR CHANCE TO PURCHASE. CALL FOR APPT. TODAY!
